*************** Rock Paper Scissors Lizzard and Spock ********************************

Game Rules:
1. Say hello (welcome Player)
2. Display rules, how it worrks
3. Let user select Game Mode and
4. Display options to players
5. Pick a Gesture from list  ********************************
    Second Player / AI
6. Compare Gesture 
   a- Same gesture - no winner
   b- Declare winner of round
   c- Give winner a point
7. Keep playing rounds until a winner is declared 
8. Declare Winner


